# HDRI Environment Maps

Place .hdr files here for realistic lighting and reflections.

## Recommended Free Sources:
- Poly Haven: https://polyhaven.com/hdris
- HDRIHaven: https://hdrihaven.com/

## Suggested HDRIs:
- abandoned_warehouse_01_1k.hdr - Dark industrial interior
- industrial_sunset_1k.hdr - Warm industrial
- empty_warehouse_01_1k.hdr - Clean factory

## Resolution:
- 1K (1024x512) is sufficient for most use cases
- 2K for higher quality reflections
- 4K only if targeting high-end displays
